# Management Layer

## Prioritization Order

```
Activation → Retention → Core Value → Conversion
```

## Planning Rhythm

- Weekly: goals → tasks → ship → review metrics
- Monthly: recalibration

## Admin Operations

- Require authorization
- Log all actions
- Strict input validation
- Audit trails → #mvp-ryla-log

## Configuration

- Environment-specific
- Never commit secrets
- Validate on startup

## Decisions

- Fast if reversible
- Document if irreversible (ADR)
- Data > opinions
- Simplicity > cleverness

## Accountability

- Clear owner per epic
- Progress = metric impact
- No blame — systems > individuals
